@node INTRO "MCC_Envelope/Introduction"

@{u}The MCC_Envelope Gadget@{uu}
This is a custom MUI gadget for editing envelopes as used by various 
MIDI synthesizers. 

Unfortunately, it is not as flexible as I would have liked. But I
haven't got unlimited time to work on this gadget so I decided to
release it as it is now.

@{b}Usage@{ub}
Simply click on one of the knobs and drag it around with the mouse. If
you click near the knob but outside the knob itself the knob will
move in steps of 1. This makes finetuning a lot easier.

@endnode

@node REQ "MCC_Envelope/Requirements"
 · An Amiga!
 · Kickstart 2.0 or better.
 · MUI v3.8 or better. (Magic User Interface)
 · At least 1MB of RAM. More is recommended.
@endnode


